00:17:08.150 --> 00:17:09.710
I sort of gave it away.

00:17:09.710 --> 00:17:13.369
Flipping in time does what to
the magnitude of the Fourier

00:17:13.369 --> 00:17:15.530
transform?

00:17:15.530 --> 00:17:18.522
Flipping time--

00:17:18.522 --> 00:17:20.144
AUDIENCE: Change the magnitude?

00:17:20.144 --> 00:17:22.310
DENNIS FREEMAN: Doesn't
